### ============================================================
### OWNERSHIP GUARD — requires seed.py to be run first
###
### Flow:
###   1. Login as Anna → paste accessToken into @annaToken
###   2. Login as Bob  → paste accessToken into @bobToken
###   3. Run the ownership tests below
### ============================================================

### Login as Anna (anna@seed.pl / AnnaTest123!)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anna@seed.pl",
  "password": "AnnaTest123!"
}

### Login as Bob (bob@seed.pl / BobTest456!)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@seed.pl",
  "password": "BobTest456!"
}

###

# Paste access tokens from login responses:
@annaToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI1ZWVkMDAwMC0wMDAwLTQwMDAtODAwMC0wMDAwMDAwMDAwMDEiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFubmFAc2VlZC5wbCIsImlhdCI6MTc3NzA2Njk2NiwiZXhwIjoxNzc3MDY3ODY2fQ.vMMYw92Ng6dPueTAe8UWNN8TOhRzXFWonJp7wpjT5i4
@bobToken  = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI1ZWVkMDAwMC0wMDAwLTAwMDAtMDAwMC0wMDAwMDAwMDAwMDIiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJvYkBzZWVkLnBsIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3MDY2NzQ0LCJleHAiOjE3NzcwNjc2NDR9.evJEnUYTn_8btNyipOZQWg0dHHJIUB2Suy85AfqvMbM
# Fixed IDs from seed.py:
@annaTemplateId = 5eed0000-0000-4002-8002-000000000001
@bobTemplateId  = 5eed0000-0000-4002-8002-000000000004
@annaLogId      = 5eed0000-0000-4003-8003-000000000001
@bobLogId       = 5eed0000-0000-4003-8003-000000000003

### ============================================================
### WORKOUT TEMPLATES — ownership
### ============================================================

### PATCH own template (Anna → Anna's) — should 200
PATCH http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/{{annaTemplateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anna Push Day v2"
}

### PATCH foreign template (Anna → Bob's) — should 403
PATCH http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/{{bobTemplateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hacked by Anna"
}

### DELETE own template (Bob → Bob's) — should 200
DELETE http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/{{bobTemplateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### DELETE foreign template (Bob → Anna's) — should 403
DELETE http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/{{annaTemplateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### GET foreign template — should still 200 (guard doesn't block reads)
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/{{bobTemplateId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### ============================================================
### WORKOUT LOGS — ownership
### ============================================================

### PATCH own log (Anna → Anna's) — should 200
PATCH http://localhost:3000/workout-logs/{{annaLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "exercises": [
    {
      "exerciseId": "5eed0000-0000-4001-8001-000000000001",
      "order": 1,
      "sets": [{ "weight": 75, "reps": 8, "rpe": 7, "order": 1 }]
    }
  ]
}

### PATCH foreign log (Anna → Bob's) — should 403
PATCH http://localhost:3000/workout-logs/{{bobLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "exercises": [
    {
      "exerciseId": "5eed0000-0000-4001-8001-000000000001",
      "order": 1,
      "sets": [{ "weight": 75, "reps": 8, "rpe": 7, "order": 1 }]
    }
  ]
}

### DELETE own log (Bob → Bob's) — should 200
DELETE http://localhost:3000/workout-logs/{{bobLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### DELETE foreign log (Bob → Anna's) — should 403
DELETE http://localhost:3000/workout-logs/{{annaLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bobToken}}

### ============================================================
### EDGE CASES
### ============================================================

### PATCH nonexistent template — should 403 (guard returns false on not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost"
}

### PATCH without auth — should 401 (JwtGuard fires before OwnershipGuard)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/workout-templates/{{annaTemplateId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No auth"
}
